  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Manual Muscle Testing -8 muscles (MMT-8). Efficacy of BAF312 will be assessed by comparing the improvements with every dose of BAF312 to that of placebo.</measure>
    <time_frame>6 months</time_frame>
    <safety_issue>No</safety_issue>
    <description>The primary aim of this study is to assess the efficacy of different doses of BAF312 on the MMT-8 after 6 months. The overall efficacy of BAF312 will be assessed by comparing the improvements of MMT-8 with every dose of BAF312 to that of placebo. Then the doseresponse curve of MMT-8 will be estimated with the aim to determine a target dose for the program.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
